posting_body: ['521 Stadium Place S, Seattle, WA 98104', 'The Wave takes modern design to new heights.', 'This 26 story apartment tower has an unparalleled look, location and breathtaking views (from up here you can see the 12th Person!).', 'The Wave is part of Stadium Place, a modern community designed so you can live, work and play in Seattle’s most famous neighborhoods.', 'The Wave luxury apartment homes offer floor to ceiling windows, top end finishes, quartz counters, air conditioning, walk in closets and wood flooring along with two roof top lounges with stunning views, a massive courtyard, high tech theater and a spa like fitness center.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Mobile Kitchen Island', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Washer and Dryer', 'Air Conditioning', 'Stainless-Steel Appliances', 'High-End Finishes', 'Community Features:', 'Resident Package Lockers', 'Private Courtyard', 'Fitness Center and Yoga Room', 'Onsite Controlled Access Parking and Storage', 'The Summit Lounge', 'Business and Conference Center', 'Guest Suite', 'Resident Lounge and Game Room', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and Availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Contact us today for the most up to date information.']
